# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Secrets / credentials  real deployed config with keys
# The repo keeps a sanitized template; actual keys must never be committed.
# If someone copies bridge_api.toml.example -> bridge_api.toml and fills in
# real credentials, this line prevents accidental commit.
# (The template itself is tracked as bridge_api.toml with placeholder values.)

